name: Last shirt.  Honest.  Tour Shirt.  Neat.
description:
Tour shirt from '09, with Splitter (rip bro's).  

Has dates on the back, from places that we played.  Probably near you.  Or maybe not.  I don't know where you live yet.  

We have two of these, super duper limited.  Large only.

name: No fuckin' way!  It's a fuckin coozie!  Coozy?  ...Coozie.
description:
This totally rad contraption is for keeping stuff cold, or hot probably, I'm not a fuckin' scientist.  It'll fit things roughly the size of a small kitten, or a medium sized kitten I guess.  Probably not a puppy.  Maybe a really small puppy.  I think an adolescent owl or other medium sized raptor would fit best.  And it would be a stylish motherfucker.  And cold.  Or warm.  Whatever temperature it started at, it would be that longer than if it was not wearing this super neat coozie.  Given the ambient temperature around it is less or greater than the temperature you want it to be.  I mean, if the temperature was more or less than what you wanted the item to be, this coozie would help keep the item at the temperature at which it began I guess is what I'm saying...  

You get the idea.

name: Psytography?  Fuckin Psytography bro!
description:
This is what it says it is!  Compact Disc.  Full of tunez.  Pretty much everything ever.  Except stuff made after 2009.  So, like, the split tape with Cemetery Rapist, that's not on this.  Also, anything with anyone singing other than Vesper, that's also not on here.  So Scott stuff, and Shank stuff, and misguided "let's totally DIY it it'll be cool."  That other stuff, totally not on it.

It is totally DIY though.  I think we have like 4 of them.  Might be a couple more.  I don't know.
